text: Ocotea oocarpa is a species of plant in the family Lauraceae. It is an evergreen tree in the genus Ocotea. It is endemic to Ecuador. Its natural habitat is subtropical or tropical moist montane forests. ==References== oocarpa Category:Endemic flora of Ecuador Category:Trees of Ecuador Category:Data deficient plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
